---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import site from '../../site.config.json';
---
<BaseLayout title="Support" description="Get help with Speech Recognition Cloud. Getting started guides, tips, troubleshooting, and FAQ.">
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:900px">
      <p class="eyebrow">SUPPORT</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:12px">How can we help?</h1>
      <p class="muted" style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:20px">Speech Recognition Cloud is a Windows voice dictation application that uses cloud-based AI to transcribe your voice to text. The transcribed text is automatically typed at your cursor in any Windows application.</p>
      <p class="muted" style="font-size:16px;margin-bottom:48px">Speech Recognition Cloud also has the ability to enhance transcriptions with AI through its <a href="/support/ai-modes" style="color:var(--brand);font-weight:600">AI Modes</a> feature.</p>

      <div class="support-grid">
        <a href="/support/getting-started" class="support-card">
          <div class="support-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4338CA" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Getting started</h3>
          <p class="muted">Install, set up your microphone, and start dictating in minutes.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/support/faq" class="support-card">
          <div class="support-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4338CA" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 015.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg></div>
          <h3>FAQ</h3>
          <p class="muted">Answers to the most common questions about Speech Recognition Cloud.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/support/troubleshooting" class="support-card">
          <div class="support-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4338CA" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Troubleshooting</h3>
          <p class="muted">Solutions for common issues with installation, microphones, and accuracy.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="how-to-use">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom:24px">How to use Speech Recognition Cloud</h2>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom:20px">Speech Recognition Cloud works in any text field in any Windows application. Word, Outlook, Chrome, EMRs, web forms, messaging apps, or anything else where you can type.</p>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step"><span class="step-num">1</span><div><p>Place your cursor in a text field where you want the text to appear</p></div></div>
          <div class="step"><span class="step-num">2</span><div><p>Press your hotkey (CapsLock by default) to start recording</p></div></div>
          <div class="step"><span class="step-num">3</span><div><p>Speak what you want to type</p></div></div>
          <div class="step"><span class="step-num">4</span><div><p>Press the hotkey again to stop recording and transcribe</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-top:16px;font-size:14px">The hotkey can be customised in Settings. Popular alternatives include F1-F12, tilde (~), Scroll Lock, or Pause.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="margin-top:48px;margin-bottom:24px">Features and guides</h2>
      <div class="support-grid">
        <a href="/support/tips" class="support-card">
          <div class="support-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4338CA" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Tips for better accuracy</h3>
          <p class="muted">Improve your dictation with microphone tips, speaking technique, and workflow advice.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/support/ai-modes" class="support-card">
          <div class="support-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4338CA" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg></div>
          <h3>AI modes</h3>
          <p class="muted">Write, Rewrite, Answer, Reply, and Run Command modes for AI-enhanced dictation.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/support/spoken-punctuation" class="support-card">
          <div class="support-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4338CA" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 7V4h16v3"/><path d="M9 20h6"/><path d="M12 4v16"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Spoken punctuation</h3>
          <p class="muted">Voice commands for punctuation, formatting, bullet points, and spelling mode.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/support/text-replacements" class="support-card">
          <div class="support-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4338CA" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 4H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-7"/><path d="M18.5 2.5a2.121 2.121 0 013 3L12 15l-4 1 1-4 9.5-9.5z"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Text replacements</h3>
          <p class="muted">Auto-replace words and phrases. Expand abbreviations, fix errors, insert templates.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/support/settings" class="support-card">
          <div class="support-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4338CA" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 00.33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 010 2.83 2 2 0 01-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 00-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 01-2 2 2 2 0 01-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 009 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 2 2 0 010-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 004.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 01-2-2 2 2 0 012-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 004.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 00-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 010-2.83 2 2 0 012.83 0l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 009 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 001-1.51V3a2 2 0 012-2 2 2 0 012 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 001 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 001.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 012.83 0 2 2 0 010 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 00-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 001.51 1H21a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 01-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 00-1.51 1z"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Settings</h3>
          <p class="muted">Configure all options: microphone, hotkeys, vocabulary, AI, preferences.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="support-card">
          <div class="support-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#4338CA" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Contact us</h3>
          <p class="muted">Can't find what you need? Get in touch and we'll help.</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="quick-tips">
        <h2 style="margin-bottom:24px">Quick tips</h2>
        <div class="tip-item"><h3>Re-paste hotkey</h3><p class="muted">Press Ctrl+Alt+V to paste the last dictated text. Useful if you forgot to place your cursor in the right field before dictating.</p></div>
        <div class="tip-item"><h3>Double-tap to send Enter</h3><p class="muted">Double-tap your hotkey to stop recording and automatically add an Enter keystroke after the transcription. Useful for sending messages in chat apps without touching your keyboard. Can be enabled in Settings.</p></div>
        <div class="tip-item"><h3>Minimise to system tray</h3><p class="muted">Click the minimise button to hide Speech Recognition Cloud to the system tray. You can also enable "Start minimised" in Settings to have it start hidden automatically.</p></div>
        <div class="tip-item"><h3>Custom vocabulary</h3><p class="muted">Add names, technical terms, and context to your vocabulary in Settings. This helps the transcription engine recognise specialised words.</p></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section-pad section-neutral">
    <div class="container text-center" style="max-width:600px">
      <h2 style="margin-bottom:12px">Still need help?</h2>
      <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom:24px">Can't find what you're looking for? Send us a message and we'll get back to you.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <style is:inline>
    .eyebrow{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--brand);letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px}
    .support-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;margin-bottom:48px}
    .support-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:28px;transition:border-color 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s,transform 0.2s;text-decoration:none;color:inherit}
    .support-card:hover{border-color:var(--brand);box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);transform:translateY(-2px)}
    .support-icon{width:48px;height:48px;background:var(--brand-lightest, #EEF2FF);border-radius:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px}
    .support-card h3{font-size:17px;margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:600}
    .support-card .muted{font-size:14px}
    .how-to-use{margin-top:48px;padding:32px;background:var(--neutral);border-radius:16px}
    .steps{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px}
    .step{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:center}
    .step-num{width:36px;height:36px;background:var(--brand);color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;flex-shrink:0}
    .step p{font-size:15px;font-weight:500}
    .quick-tips{margin-top:48px}
    .tip-item{margin-bottom:16px;padding:16px 20px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px}
    .tip-item h3{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px}
    .tip-item .muted{font-size:14px;line-height:1.6}
    @media(max-width:768px){.support-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
